Class Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.models.JsonModel
      • net.dean.jraw.models.RedditObject
        • net.dean.jraw.models.Thing
          • net.dean.jraw.models.Contribution
            • net.dean.jraw.models.Message
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Created, Distinguishable, JsonAttribute
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommentMessage, PrivateMessage

    @Model(kind=ABSTRACT,
       serializer=MessageSerializer.class)
public abstract class Message
extends Contribution
implements Distinguishable
    This class represents any data that can appear in a user's inbox. The two main subclasses of this class are PrivateMessage (for when a user contacts another user directly) and CommentMessage (for when a user replies to another user's comment).
